{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9e56c46cca","title":"中共中央关于在批林批孔运动中对外宾、外交官员和在华外国工作、学习人员有关“四大”的几项规定（草案）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4f611b5fca","index":0,"year":1974,"month":2,"day":14,"articleId":"9e56c46cca","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"f10c9d6647","name":"中共中央"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b083ad2c24","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于在批林批孔运动中对外宾、外交官员和在华外国工作、学习人员有关“四大”的几项规定（草案）","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e56c46cca","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6851db3156","type":"paragraph","text":"中发[1974]6号","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e56c46cca","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b817fe0fbf","type":"paragraph","text":"中共中央通知","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e56c46cca","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"63a6bde30a","type":"paragraph","text":"一、凡是外宾、外国旅游者、外国记者、外国文化团、外国专家及其家属、外国留学生，开放城市、厂矿、学校、旅社、服务机构以及接待参观的地区和单位，有问到当前批林批孔等问题，应按中央有关文件和人民日报社论的方针和口径答复。如要求去看公开场所写出的大字报，应允许他们阅读，如涉及内部情况的大字报，应另辟一处，不对外开放。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e56c46cca","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9c10952cfe","type":"paragraph","text":"二、在上述所有人员，凡持有照相机、录像机、录音机、电影机、电视机的，均须取得我方接待人员的同意，方可摄影、录音，否则我方有权干涉。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e56c46cca","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b9f8ab8402","type":"paragraph","text":"三、各单位、地区张贴出的大字报，除中央另有规定外，一般不许抄贴中央文件。大字报、大辩论，均不许泄露国家机密，如国家计划数字、财政支出、外交机密、国防机密等。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e56c46cca","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e7840ca429","type":"paragraph","text":" \t中 共 中 央","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e56c46cca","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9e4a02545b","type":"paragraph","text":"一九七四年二月十四日","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e56c46cca","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ef0d4f05f7","type":"paragraph","text":"（发至省、军级）","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e56c46cca","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f17013da14","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：根据文件的翻印件打印","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9e56c46cca","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}